site_name: Land bound by Vincent Road, Wilmount Street and Woolwich New Road, Woolwich, SE18
description: Demolition of the existing buildings and structure and the phased redevelopment of the site for a mixed-use scheme comprising a multipurpose leisure centre (Class F2), commercial and business uses (Class E), residential dwellings (Class C3), new public square and new public realm with hard and soft landscape works, highways works, parking, access and servicing arrangements, and associated works.
